    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 guidance. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Project requirements PR-HEM-001 through PR-HEM-007 are addressed in the supporting technical report and the model output meets the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all evaluated operating points.",
